<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>همُ الْفَتَى الْمَاجِدُ الْغَطْرِيفِ مَكْرمةٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَضُوع نَادِي الْمَلا مِنْ نَشْرِهَا الْعِطْر<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَحِلْيَة الْمَرْءِ فَي كَسْبِ الْمَحَامِد لا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَي نَظْمِ عَقْدٍ مِنَ الْعِقْيَانِ وَالدُّرَرِِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تَكْسُو الْمَحَامِدُ وَجْه الْمَرْءِ بَهْجَتهَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>كَمَا اكْتَسَى الزَّهْرُ زَهْرَ الرَّوْضِ بِالْمَطَرِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>يَخْلُدُ الذِّكْر حَمْدًا طَابَ مَنْشؤه<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَلَيْسَ يَمْحُو الْمَزَايا سَالِفَ الْعَصْرِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَميز النَّاس بِالْفَضْلِ الْمُبِينِ كَمَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>تَمَيَّزُوا بَيْنَهُمْ فِي خَلْقِهِ الصُّورِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِقَدْرِ مَعْرِفَةِ الإِنْسَان قِيمَتُهُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَبِالْفَضْلِ كَانَ الْفَرْقُ فِي الْبَشَرِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مَا الْفَضْلُ فِي بَزّةِ تَزْهُو بِرَوْنَقِهَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَأَيُّ فَضْلٍ لا برِيزٍ عَلَى مَدَرِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَإِنَّمَا الْفَضْلُ فِي عِلْمٍ وَفِي أَدَبٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَفِي مَكَارِمٍ تَجْلُو صِدْق مُفْتَخَرِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَلا تَسَاو بِأَخْلاقٍ مُهَذَّبَة<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَخْلاق سُوءٍ أَتَتْ مِنْ سَارِحِ الْبَقَرِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَخُذْ بِمَنْهَجِ مَنْ يَعْصِي هَوَاهُ وَقَدْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أَطَاعَ أَهْلَ الْحِجَا فِي كُلِّ مُؤْتَمَرِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>إِنَّ الْهَوَى يُفْسِدُ الْعَقْلَ السَّلِيمِ وَمَنْ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>يَعْصِي الْهَوَى عَاشَ فِي أَمْنٍ مِنَ الضَّرَرِ<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>